{"tid":1885802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港人口突破750萬 去年有3.9萬人持單程證來港","createTime":"2020-02-18T14:07:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T02:02:48.000Z","uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6adc53ae2720fee941c5e8705e732d38d50895f3","tid":1885802,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:07:48.000Z","msg":"統計處最新公佈本港人口數字，截至去年底本港人口突破750萬，臨時數字為750萬700人，按年增長約0.2%，期內人口淨增加約1.42萬人。同時，去年持單程證來港定居人數為3.91萬人，數字屬2015年以來低位，平均每日約107人來港，佔每日150個名額的71.3%。<br />\n<br />\n統計處最新數字顯示，去年全年本港有5.29萬人出生，期內死亡人數為4.85萬人；至於利用單程證遷入香港的新移民人數為3.91萬人，同期間其他香港居民則為2.92萬人，總計香港人口達到750萬700人。若將人口進一步劃分，去年底本港「常住人口」約為730.35萬人，按年增長約0.6%；而流動人口則為19.72萬人，按年減幅達13.7%。去年底本港流動人口數字，亦是自2002年以來最低。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200218/KL7A2BOBUUM2LOQMWYAJRL3QWM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200218%2FKL7A2BOBUUM2LOQMWYAJRL3QWM%2F&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=5658a1cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200218%2FKL7A2BOBUUM2LOQMWYAJRL3QWM%2F&h=031ae790\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200218/KL7A2BOBUUM2LOQMWYAJRL3QWM/</a>"},{"pid":"9f4ec81562c66567b370cf17d0a5ad9156488c32","tid":1885802,"uid":4964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:09:46.000Z","msg":"中共:普選?好呀,我洗夠人口儲夠票咪恩賜比你囉"},{"pid":"94882a53641d1dbbb3cbaa6e161e9ce44a6990e1","tid":1885802,"uid":346806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:14:32.000Z","msg":"可能2019年下半年少咗人<br />\n點都好，大家要加油，堅持抗爭<br />\n反共爭取普選"},{"pid":"d501fec1d5bfcf330a4ffbc13098078e76528931","tid":1885802,"uid":100337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T01:12:27.000Z","msg":"48500死亡人口有幾多係被自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e20ff786a8abce2d31f32c665357038fb2bc776","tid":1885802,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislik